Layering is key to ultra black eyeliner! 👀
Start with a non waterproof pencil - my fav is @westmanatelier EyeLove You Pencil in Khol Noir, smudge and shape with @lymakeupartist LY17 Brush then sharpen with @biodermausa Micellar and @daiso_usa  Pointed cotton buds, then blot with tissue, set with a very light layer of translucent powder, add a waterproof pencil @milanicosmetics StAy Put Pencil doesn’t budge! Finally I top with a water activated black liner(this ones from the lab) -  @mattelashes makes a good one, or use your favorite liquid liner, @danessa_myricks paint, @painted.co paint or @inglot_cosmetics Gel makes an incredible long last black gel liner. 👁️ Shadow @danessa_myricks Lightworks Volume V Evolving
💋 Lips @charlottetilbury Foxy Brown Lipliner and @nimya She Said What LipGloss ✨

1920’s Vintage Maybelline EyeShadow with a box! 🤩 @maybelline this has been archived and won’t be touched again until its put on display! Huge thanks again to Misty Grennell - I’ve linked some of her other vintage makeup items in my stories 😃 you can buy from eBay!

There is so much more to share about legendary makeup artist Marie Irvine. She not only worked with marilyn monroe but also the beatles, jane fonda, vivienne leigh, the Queen mother - she created editorials with iconic photographers Irving Penn, Richard Avedon, John Rawlings, Milton Greene and more! Thankyou all for celebrating this wonderful artist - I’m so glad she got to see all of your responses before she passed 🥲
